section.section:
The notice under this subsection shall:
state the estimated economic impact of the proposed regulation on:
the revenues and expenditures of units of the State government and of local government units; and
groups such as consumer, industry, taxpayer, or trade groups;
include a statement of purpose;
satisfy the requirements of § 2-1505.2 of this article;
comply with § 7-113(c) of the Human Services Article; and
give persons an opportunity to comment before adoption of the proposed regulation, by:
setting a date, time, and place for a public hearing at which oral or written views and information may be submitted; or
giving a telephone number that a person may call to comment and an address to which a person may send comments.
